---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Enquiry received | Sky Lavelle"
  description="Your enquiry has been received."
  noindex
>
  <section class="section min-h-[60vh] flex items-center">
    <div class="container max-w-2xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-emerald-100 mb-6">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-emerald-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-warm-900 mb-3">Enquiry received.</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-warm-700">
          A response will come within one business day. If the situation is urgent, note that in your message.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg border border-warm-200 bg-warm-50 p-6 mb-6">
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-warm-900 mb-2">What happens next</h2>
        <ol class="space-y-2 text-sm text-warm-800">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-warm-800 text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">1</span>
            Your enquiry is reviewed and you receive a written response within one business day.
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-warm-800 text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">2</span>
            If there is a clear fit, a short call is usually the next step to scope the engagement.
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-warm-800 text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">3</span>
            Advisory engagements are scoped after the initial conversation. There is no standard package imposed on every situation.
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        <a href="https://lavelleptyltd.com.au/pmo-resources" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group flex flex-col p-5 rounded-lg border border-warm-200 bg-white hover:border-ochre-400 transition-colors">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-warm-900 group-hover:text-ochre-600 mb-1">Lavelle Pty Ltd resources</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-warm-700 flex-1">PMO templates, free tools and delivery resources for project managers and delivery leads.</p>
          <span class="mt-3 text-sm font-medium text-ochre-600">Browse resources &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/articles" class="group flex flex-col p-5 rounded-lg border border-warm-200 bg-white hover:border-ochre-400 transition-colors">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-warm-900 group-hover:text-ochre-600 mb-1">Articles</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-warm-700 flex-1">Practical guides on the most common challenges in enterprise technology delivery.</p>
          <span class="mt-3 text-sm font-medium text-ochre-600">Browse articles &rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
